Package: nif
Title: Construct NONMEM input files from SDTM data
Version: 0.50.14
Authors@R: 
    person("Rainer", "Strotmann", , "rainer.strotmann@mailbox.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A system to import and explore Study Data Tabulation Model
    (SDTM) formatted data from clinical studies, and to create and explore
    NONMEM Input File (NIF) data sets from them that can be used for
    pharmacometric analyses.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/rstrotmann/nif,
    https://rstrotmann.github.io/nif/reference/index.html
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
